JOHANNESBURG - As Youth Month draws to a close, we spoke to some young book worms to find out what they're reading.Click on the above video to see reporter Lindiwe Sithole talk to the little bookworms about their favourite reads. The second video is about Pamela Ngubeni who wrote a book on bullying.The young girl says she never intended writing the book, she was just journaling her experiences as she had no one to share it with. eNCA